Regex search tricks
--------------------------------------------------------

1)
Search from a wild char to the end of the line.

Example: * or / to the end of line
[*/].*$

Example: remove all wild chars to end line, commonly used in converting ublock filters to domains. Excluding * and @
[/^$ ].*$

2) Remove random lines matching certain characters
Use search and bookmark the lines
Then View -> Bookmark -> Remove bookmarked lines

